  <p class="mb-4">
    Blue Guardian offers six challenge types spread across instant and traditional evaluation models. Each model has different rules for payout, drawdown, and account progression. While the variety gives you plenty of choice, the structure can be inconsistent — especially between Instant Starter, Instant Standard, and the Three Step options. If you're considering this firm, it's worth paying close attention to the fine print on payout caps, consistency rules, and account closure triggers.
  </p>

  <!-- Quick stats -->
  <div class="grid grid-cols-2 sm:grid-cols-4 gap-3 mb-8">
    <div class="rounded-lg bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 px-3 py-2.5 text-center">
