      <p>A single-use option that gives you a $5,000 funded account upfront with no profit target. No evaluation phase, but payouts are capped — you can only withdraw once, and the maximum payout is $250. Once that withdrawal is made, the account is closed permanently.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-red-600 font-semibold mt-1">One payout only. Max $250. Account closes after withdrawal. 15% consistency rule.</p>
