      <p>Single-phase evaluation with no deadlines. Hit the profit target and you're eligible for a funded account. Static drawdowns: 3% daily and 6% total. Refundable fee returned after your fourth payout. Payouts every 7 days once funded.</p>
      <p class="text-xs text-emerald-600 font-semibold mt-1">Up to 90% profit split. Refundable fee. No time limit.</p>
