      <p>A three-phase structure (despite the "Two Step" name). Step 1 and 2 are challenges, Step 3 is the funded phase. Higher drawdowns at 8% total and 4% daily. Fixed 10% profit target for Phase 1. Bi-weekly payouts at 90% split.</p>
